<title>PHILIPPINES: Grand Plaza taps HK hotelier as manager.</title>
<headline>Grand Plaza taps HK hotelier as manager.</headline>
<dateline>MANILA 1997-04-17</dateline>
<text>
<p>Grand Plaza Hotel Corp said on Thursday its board had approved a five-year management contract with CDL Hotels International Ltd of Hong Kong.</p>
<p>&quot;The management agreement has standard renewal term and is subject to payment of management and technical assistance fees,&quot; legal counsel Christopher Lim told the Philippine Stock Exchange.</p>
<p>CDL is the hotel arm of Singapore's City Developments Ltd.</p>
<p>Grand Plaza Hotel Corp owns one deluxe hotel in the Philippines.</p>
